288
00:14:26.082 --> 00:14:28.649
Positive.

289
00:14:28.650 --> 00:14:29.998
Bex?

290
00:14:34.961 --> 00:14:36.613
I've always dreamed
of falling in love with...

291
00:14:36.614 --> 00:14:38.441
