non-dangerous accountant.

339
00:17:19.690 --> 00:17:21.909
Except for the fact
that her husband actually

340
00:17:21.910 --> 00:17:23.389
suddenly passed
six months before

341
00:17:23.390 --> 00:17:24.564
she started working
with Marsden.

342
00:17:24.565 --> 00:17:26.261
With that kind of tragedy.
who knows

343
00:17:26.262 --> 00:17:27.654
