346
00:17:31.963 --> 00:17:33.790
- She's got a son.
- She's got a son.

347
00:17:35.793 --> 00:17:37.142
Did you guys plan that?

348
00:17:43.323 --> 00:17:44.714
What are we really
hoping to get

349
