360
00:18:19.315 --> 00:18:21.229
- What?
- Not like that.

361
00:18:32.285 --> 00:18:34.982
I didn't even do anything!

362
00:18:34.983 --> 00:18:36.810
Why'd you run?

363
00:18:36.811 --> 00:18:38.028
Nice of you to show up.

364
00:18:38.029 --> 00:18:39.682
