No. my first time in Salt Lake.

384
00:19:46.489 --> 00:19:51.754
Just have...
one of those faces.

385
00:19:51.755 --> 00:19:53.452
I think we're all set.

386
00:19:53.453 --> 00:19:54.670
Mm-hmm.

387
00:19:54.671 --> 00:19:56.716
