519
00:26:48.084 --> 00:26:49.650
Hold up.

520
00:26:49.651 --> 00:26:52.435
Whoa!

521
00:26:52.436 --> 00:26:54.176
Mark.

522
00:26:54.177 --> 00:26:56.483
